      <title>特朗普的交易被颠覆了，因为国债返回击败了我们的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/treasuries-are-beating-us-stocks-for-first-time-since-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普当选总统以来，美国国债现在胜过股票，一些战略家说，这些收益的空间可以运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/treasuries-are-beating-us-stocks-for-first-time-since-trump-win</guid>
